auto lo
iface lo inet loopback

iface eno1 inet manual

auto vmbr0
iface vmbr0 inet manual
    bridge-ports eno1
    bridge-stp off
    bridge-fd 0
    bridge-vlan-aware yes
    bridge-vids 2-4094

auto vmbr0.10
iface vmbr0.10 inet static
    address 10.10.10.10/24
    gateway 10.10.10.1

# Example notes:
# - vmbr0 is the primary bridge attached to the physical NIC
# - VLAN-aware mode allows guest tagging across the bridge
# - vmbr0.10 is the management interface for the Proxmox host
# - Guest VMs can be assigned VLAN tags such as 20 or 30 in Proxmox

# Replace:
# - eno1 with your actual physical NIC
# - 10.10.10.10/24 with your actual Proxmox management address
# - 10.10.10.1 with the pfSense gateway for the management VLAN
